{
  "stem": "3524.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At one period before we docked in Scotland we were told to sleep with our clothes on and keep a life preserver nearby.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we found out later that the submarines were following the ship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the carried a rather large contingency.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I'm sure that had they had the opportunity, they would have loved to have made that a target.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But fortunately, nothing ever transpired in that respect.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We landed in Lockerbie-- no, not-- I'm thinking of the plane-- the plane.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We landed in northern Scotland-- I can't remember the exact town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were immediately entrained and went almost the length of the British islands down to Tenby, South Wales.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we arrived there the day before Christmas, 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were pretty much put right on the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only personnel that we had contact with were Red Cross gals who gave coffee, and donuts, and refreshments of one type or another.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we had not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were going to await further instructions at Tenby and continue some training at that point.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many of the personnel were, depending upon their specialty, were sent out to regional hospitals in England to receive further training, for example, x-ray and lab.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of the nurses were sent to do ward work in some of the hospitals there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because my work had been in the dispensary, I and the other pharmacists remained there in the dispensary in the-- to service the medical-- immediate medical needs of our own unit.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's a little bit of a lonely one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in a way, it was a sense of adventure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The inhabitants of the town were extremely nice to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they celebrated Christmas more like we celebrate New Year's Eve.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
